=content_for(:page_title, "Projects")
.row
  .col-sm-2
    %ul.nav.nav-pills.nav-stacked
      - projects.each do |key, title|
        %li{ class: project == key && 'active' }
          %a{ href: projects_path(project: key) }= title

  .col-sm-10
    - if project
      .project
        = render partial: project
    - else
      %p.welcome
        These are some of the personal (i.e. non-work related) coding projects I've played with.
        Some are old and the coding quality varies as I've learnt new things or got carried away with an idea.

      .alert.alert-info
        NB: Nearly all of these should be considered work in progress or libraries of old code for me to easily reference and recall.

